Thu Jul 05, 2012	Bone in my Swamp

A shrimper claims to find a human bone in his fishing net; a man and his nephew get in a heated argument over crab traps; and water-patrol deputies investigate a strange report involving a mysterious ball of light.

Thu Jul 05, 2012	Poached

An officer attempts to resolve a bitter dispute between two neighbors in the bayou; alligator poachers are hunted in the swamp.
